<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:08:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴勒斯坦-以色列和平活动家二人组被《时代》杂志评为年度女性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-israeli-peace-activist-duo-named-among-time-magazines-women-of-the-year/0000018d-f04a-dd0a-afcf-ffde7c740000</link><description>“妇女争取和平”和“太阳妇女”这两个组织形成了所谓的“伙伴关系协定”，誓言“坚定、坚持和相互尊重地共同努力”，以结束以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:42:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-israeli-peace-activist-duo-named-among-time-magazines-women-of-the-year/0000018d-f04a-dd0a-afcf-ffde7c740000</guid></item><item><title>《欣快感》明星在接受拜登采访时抗议以色列和加沙战争时被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/euphoria-star-arrested-while-protesting-against-israel-war-in-gaza-at-biden-interview/0000018d-efd4-dd0a-afcf-efd698060000</link><description>在 JVP Instagram 上分享的一篇帖子中，亨特·谢弗 (Hunter Schafer) 与其他示威者坐在一起，身穿印有“立即停火”字样的 T 恤。该组织还发布了抗议视频，视频中女演员和其他人高呼“不再有武器，不再有战争，停火是我们奋斗的目标”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/euphoria-star-arrested-while-protesting-against-israel-war-in-gaza-at-biden-interview/0000018d-efd4-dd0a-afcf-efd698060000</guid></item><item><title>向以色列高等法院提交请愿书，反对教育部长不授予以色列奖的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/high-court-petition-filed-against-education-ministers-decision-not-to-award-israel-prize/0000018d-f01e-dd8a-a5af-f87e2cb70000</link><description>请愿书认为，根据以色列奖项规定，教育部长无权取消奖项类别。 “对这些决定的唯一不幸的解释是教育部长接管该奖项的尝试是完全不可接受的”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/high-court-petition-filed-against-education-ministers-decision-not-to-award-israel-prize/0000018d-f01e-dd8a-a5af-f87e2cb70000</guid></item><item><title>该国的宗教右翼意识形态正在以色列造成劳动力紧缩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/the-states-religious-right-ideology-is-creating-a-labor-crunch-in-israel/0000018d-f032-d7f4-a3dd-f63ee6870000</link><description>多年来，以色列经济的快速增长是由稳定增长的劳动力市场推动的。现在政府似乎正在竭尽全力缩小规模</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/the-states-religious-right-ideology-is-creating-a-labor-crunch-in-israel/0000018d-f032-d7f4-a3dd-f63ee6870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列顶级厨师开设特拉维夫最好的冰淇淋店</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/food/2024-02-28/ty-article-review/.premium/have-you-already-tasted-tel-avivs-best-ice-cream-place/0000018d-efc3-d1e0-a1dd-fff7da3f0000</link><description>洋甘菊黑胡椒、薰衣草蜂蜜和烤米饭：厨师 Eyal Shani 的新冰淇淋吧提供城里最好的冰淇淋（而且排得很长）</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:09:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/food/2024-02-28/ty-article-review/.premium/have-you-already-tasted-tel-avivs-best-ice-cream-place/0000018d-efc3-d1e0-a1dd-fff7da3f0000</guid></item><item><title>“当我的演讲被称为反犹太主义时，我感到震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-my-speech-was-called-antisemitic-i-was-shocked/0000018d-efc4-dd8a-a5af-effe1d7c0000</link><description>获得柏林电影节最佳纪录片奖本应是以色列电影制片人尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕职业生涯的顶峰。对《No Other Land》获奖感言的回应让他感到震惊，但他并没有陷入沉默</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:27:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-my-speech-was-called-antisemitic-i-was-shocked/0000018d-efc4-dd8a-a5af-effe1d7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙北部战斗中丧生的以色列军官的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-two-israeli-officers-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-ef6e-d401-a3dd-ef7e03ae0000</link><description>Iftah Shahar 少校，25 岁​​，Cap。吉瓦蒂旅 24 岁的伊泰·赛义夫 (Itai Seif) 在简易爆炸装置被触发时身亡。以色列国防军称，另外七名士兵也在爆炸中受重伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:17:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-two-israeli-officers-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-ef6e-d401-a3dd-ef7e03ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列地方选举：极端正统派、极右派在全国各地取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-local-elections-ultra-orthodox-far-right-make-gains-across-country/0000018d-eec3-d7f4-a3dd-eecfa37b0000</link><description>极端正统派和极右宗教犹太复国主义政党将在耶路撒冷取得压倒性胜利，而南部城市米兹佩·拉蒙将迎来一位以极右观点闻名的利库德集团市长。特拉维夫和海法仍然是自由派的据点</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-local-elections-ultra-orthodox-far-right-make-gains-across-country/0000018d-eec3-d7f4-a3dd-eecfa37b0000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列定居者因西岸暴力风险将继续被拘留，未经审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-settler-to-remain-in-detention-without-trial-over-risk-of-violence/0000018d-ee97-d05b-addd-ee97659c0000</link><description>以色列国防部长决定，由于阿里尔·达尼诺 (Ariel Danino) 可能在约旦河西岸煽动暴力，继 10 月份初次拘留后，将再对其实施行政拘留三个月</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:51:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-settler-to-remain-in-detention-without-trial-over-risk-of-violence/0000018d-ee97-d05b-addd-ee97659c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯之间的人质释放、停火谈判立场如何？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/where-do-the-hostage-release-talks-between-israel-and-hamas-stand-what-are-the-gaps/0000018d-ec6b-dd0a-afcf-efff7b040000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯都有兴趣在下个月斋月开始前达成释放人质的协议，但尽管最近几天的乐观情绪仍然存在，但仍然存在许多障碍</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/where-do-the-hostage-release-talks-between-israel-and-hamas-stand-what-are-the-gaps/0000018d-ec6b-dd0a-afcf-efff7b040000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列国防军坦克至少五次错误地向以色列领土开火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-tanks-mistakenly-fired-inside-israeli-territory-at-least-five-times-since-start-of-war/0000018d-eb5e-d401-a3dd-eb5e50570000</link><description>有一次，以色列和黎巴嫩边境沿线的哈尼塔集体农场发射了两枚炮弹，炸毁了两栋房屋；另一次，在加沙发射的一枚炮弹击中了斯德洛特市政厅。以色列国防军回应：“吸取了必要的教训”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-tanks-mistakenly-fired-inside-israeli-territory-at-least-five-times-since-start-of-war/0000018d-eb5e-d401-a3dd-eb5e50570000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人呼吁在斋月期间向阿克萨清真寺进军；两名以色列国防军士兵在加沙丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-live/sirens-sound-in-southern-israel-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon/0000018d-ed87-d7f4-a3dd-ef8fa5460000</link><description>什莫纳市建筑遭黎巴嫩发射袭击 ■ 拜登表示，他希望下周能达成停火协议 ■ 消息人士称，哈马斯正在研究巴黎停火提案，涉及 40 天停火和交换人质 ■ 哈马斯卫生部称加沙最后一天有96人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:25:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-live/sirens-sound-in-southern-israel-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon/0000018d-ed87-d7f4-a3dd-ef8fa5460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列第一家 Shake Shack 在特拉维夫开业，但理由并不稳固</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-first-shake-shack-opens-in-tel-aviv-on-shaky-grounds/0000018d-eb52-d1e0-a1dd-fbf7b4190000</link><description>在支持巴勒斯坦的呼吁抵制以及细心的犹太人的失望叹息中，以色列获得了第一个 Shake Shack 汉堡店，这让我们的记者回忆起更简单、更奶酪的时代</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:45:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-first-shake-shack-opens-in-tel-aviv-on-shaky-grounds/0000018d-eb52-d1e0-a1dd-fbf7b4190000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间以色列地方选举投票率低，公众冷漠</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/low-turnout-in-israels-local-elections-amid-war-in-gaza-public-apathy/0000018d-ec43-d05b-addd-eec305be0000</link><description>全天投票率仍然很低，只有不到一半的合格选民投票</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/low-turnout-in-israels-local-elections-amid-war-in-gaza-public-apathy/0000018d-ec43-d05b-addd-eec305be0000</guid></item><item><title>这个斋月，以色列极右翼部长会放火还是会被遏制？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-27/ty-article/.highlight/this-ramadan-will-israels-far-right-ministers-set-fires-or-be-reined-in/0000018d-ebc0-d401-a3dd-ebda30fd0000</link><description>用你自己的混合比喻来说，看起来这种噪音不会在基地门口停止，格兰特先生。是时候遏制你们党的领导人拉拢的不负责任的行为者了</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 19:51:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-27/ty-article/.highlight/this-ramadan-will-israels-far-right-ministers-set-fires-or-be-reined-in/0000018d-ebc0-d401-a3dd-ebda30fd0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 144 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-144/0000018d-eb6f-d401-a3dd-eb7f2a0f0000</link><description>拜登：如果达成释放人质/停火协议，以色列愿意在斋月期间停止加沙战斗，希望下周一能达成协议 ■ 一位以色列高级消息人士告诉美国广播公司新闻，内塔尼亚胡总理对拜登的言论感到惊讶 ■ 哈马斯官员称该组织正在研究巴黎制定的最新提案，但双方之间仍存在巨大差距 ■ 这是战争开始 144 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-144/0000018d-eb6f-d401-a3dd-eb7f2a0f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登可以依靠这两位以色列政客作为他的盟友吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/can-biden-depend-on-these-two-israeli-politicians-to-be-his-allies/0000018d-eacb-d7f4-a3dd-eecfb42b0000</link><description>本尼·甘茨和加迪·艾森科特加入了以色列战时内阁，忙于减少错误决策并防止鲁莽决策。但他们现在会支持拜登对加沙和该地区的愿景，还是成为内塔尼亚胡的全职帮凶？</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/can-biden-depend-on-these-two-israeli-politicians-to-be-his-allies/0000018d-eacb-d7f4-a3dd-eecfb42b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于流离失所的以色列青少年来说，荒野是寻找自我的完美场所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-israeli-teens-the-wilderness-is-proving-a-perfect-place-to-find-themselves/0000018d-ea2a-dc4b-a1cd-fb2f759e0000</link><description>约20万以色列人因战争而被疏散，青少年在孤立、焦虑和抑郁中挣扎。一项新举措旨在帮助他们逃离大自然</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 15:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-israeli-teens-the-wilderness-is-proving-a-perfect-place-to-find-themselves/0000018d-ea2a-dc4b-a1cd-fb2f759e0000</guid></item><item><title>因恐怖袭击在以色列服无期徒刑的巴勒斯坦作家获得阿拉伯文学最高奖提名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-writer-jailed-in-israel-for-bombing-is-nominated-for-top-arab-literature-prize/0000018d-eab9-dc4b-a1cd-fbbdd23b0000</link><description>出生于纳布卢斯的巴森·卡达吉 (Basem Khadaqji) 于 2005 年因协助一名在特拉维夫杀害三名以色列人的自杀式炸弹袭击者而被定罪，在手稿被偷运出狱后，他在狱中出版了至少六本书</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-writer-jailed-in-israel-for-bombing-is-nominated-for-top-arab-literature-prize/0000018d-eab9-dc4b-a1cd-fbbdd23b0000</guid></item><item><title>右翼 MKs 不顾专业人士的意见，通过新法律扩大本·格维尔的权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mks-moving-to-extend-ben-gvirs-authority-with-new-law/0000018d-ea6c-d409-a1ff-ef7eb62d0000</link><description>根据该提案，国家安全部长将能够宣布一群人为犯罪组织，并让他们没收资产。司法部警告该法律将过多权力集中于一个政府机构</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:26:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mks-moving-to-extend-ben-gvirs-authority-with-new-law/0000018d-ea6c-d409-a1ff-ef7eb62d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>